text: Thomas Siani (born 5 September 1960) is a Cameroonian former cyclist. He competed in the individual road race event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:Cameroonian male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Cameroon Category:Cyclists at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
